'''Amal Bedjaoui''' (wavutse ku ya 27 Nyakanga 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime yo muri [[Alijeriya]], producer, n'umwanditsi<ref>Amal Bedjaoui - Person sheet on Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › people</ref>.

Yavukiye muri Algiers, yize ibijyanye no gukina filime muri kaminuza ya New York <ref>Amal Bedjaoui | BFI <nowiki>https://www2.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › movies-tv-people</ref>. Yarangije muri Institut des hautes études cinématographiques hanyuma abona Master of Advanced Studies in Sinema muri kaminuza ya Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne mu 1987<ref>A Son de Amal Bedjaoui (2003) - UniFrance <nowiki>https://en.unifrance.org</nowiki> › movie › a-son</ref>.  Amaze imyaka itari mike akora nk'umuyobozi wungirije akaba n'umuyobozi ushinzwe gutunganya amafilime y kandi nk'umuyobozi wungirije ushinzwe ibikino<ref>Amal Bedjaoui - AlloCiné <nowiki>https://www.allocine.fr</nowiki> › person</ref>. Filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Une vue imprenable'', yasohotse mu 1993. Filime ye ya kabiri ngufi, ''Shoot me Angel'', yasohotse mu 1995<ref>Amal Bedjaoui - Listal <nowiki>https://www.listal.com</nowiki> › amal-bedjaoui</ref> .ahabwa igihembo cya Panorama mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Berlin<ref>Amal Bedjaoui — The Movie Database (TMDb) <nowiki>https://www.themoviedb.org</nowiki> › 1144674-amal-bedjaoui</ref> . 

Mu 2002, yashinze isosiyete ikora filimi ya ML Productions. Umwaka ukurikira, yayoboye kandi akora firime yiminota 58 ''Un Fils''<ref>Un fils d'Amal Bedjaoui - Algeriades <nowiki>http://www.algeriades.com</nowiki> › article</ref> .  ''Un fils'' ivuga amateka ya Selim, indaya y'umusore n'umubano we na madamu mukuru.<ref>Amal Bedjaoui: her biography, filmography, and some photos <nowiki>https://www.cinefil.com</nowiki> › Actor</ref>  Igice kinini cya firime gihinduranya hagati y'umunsi usanzwe kumanywa, nka Selim guhura na se, hamwe nijoro aho ubushakashatsi bwerekeranye nigitsina. Yavuzwe nk "icyitegererezo cy’ubwenegihugu bushingiye ku gitsina<ref>Bedjaoui, Amal [WorldCat Identities] <nowiki>http://worldcat.org</nowiki> › identities › viaf-52019098</ref>." Bedjaoui ni umukobwa wumudiplomate akaba n'umunyapolitiki Mohammed Bedjaoui <ref>Amal Bedjaoui - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › cast › amal-bedja...</ref>. 
